---
title: "Home"
layout: layouts/home.njk
eleventyNavigation:
  key: Home
  order: 1
numberOfLatestPostsToShow: 6
numberOfLatestVideosToShow: 3
---

<h1 class="center">Andrew Ford is the host of Code with Andrew Ford, a YouTube channel dedicated to teaching people how to code. </h1>
<h2 class="center secondary">He is also a full-stack web developer and an educator living in Tauranga, New Zealand.</h2>

<section class="latest-articles-videos">
  {%- if collections.articles.length > 0 -%}
    <article class="latest-articles">
      <h3>Latest Articles</h3>
      <ul class="article-list">
        {%- for article in collections.articles | reverse -%}
          {% set absolutePostUrl %}{{ article.url | url | absoluteUrl(metadata.url) }}{% endset %}
          {%- if article.data.draft == false and loop.index <= numberOfLatestPostsToShow -%}
            <li class="article-list-item">
              <h4 class="article-title">
                <a href="{{ absolutePostUrl }}">{{ article.data.title }}</a>
              </h4>
              <p class="article-description">{{ article.data.description }}</p>
            </li>
          {%- endif -%}
        {%- endfor %}
        <li class="article-list-item">
          <h4 class="article-title">
            <a href="{{ metadata.url }}/article/">More Articles&#8230;</a>
          </h4>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </article>
  {%- endif -%}

  {%- if latestVideos.videos.length > 0 -%}
    <aside class="latest-videos">
      <h3>Latest Videos</h3>
      <ul class="article-list">
        {%- for video in latestVideos.videos -%}
          {% if loop.index <= numberOfLatestVideosToShow -%}
            <li class="article-list-item">
              <img src="{{ video.snippet.thumbnails.medium.url }}" alt="{{ "Thumb for " + video.snippet.title }}" class="video-thumb" height="207" width="368">
              <h4 class="article-title">
                <a href={{ "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=" + video.id.videoId }}>
                  {{ video.snippet.title }}
                </a>
              </h4>
              <p class="article-description">{{ video.snippet.description }}</p>
            </li>
          {%- endif -%}
        {%- endfor -%}
        <li class="article-list-item">
          <h4 class="article-title">
          <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@CodewithAndrewFord">More Videos&#8230;</a>
          </h4>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </aside>
  {%- endif -%}

</section>